 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halle_Berry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Halle_Berry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was seen beaming and waving to onlookers while holding the Olympic torch, wearing a white tracksuit.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rap legend is one of the final torchbearers ahead of today's opening ceremony in the French capital after the torch relay ends at the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5055041576922338, \"rank\": 0.6209827473241866, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry, this video is not available any more.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The flame's journey across France began when the torch touched down in May in Marseille and the rapper will be escorting the flame on its last leg of the journey.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998431826621, \"rank\": 9.11961432458079e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.999970578957688, \"rank\": 2.9421907409177628e-05, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not the only celebrity bestowed with the honour as he was accompanied by French actress Laetitia Casta, French rapper MC Solaar, and retired Ukrainian pole-vaulter Sergey Bubka.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5055041576922338, \"rank\": 0.6209827473241866, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\", \"score\": 0.7317059375234348, \"rank\": 0.3666654790938078, \"text\": \"Laetitia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laetitia_Corbin_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casta\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casta\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5055041576922338, \"rank\": 0.6209827473241866, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MC_Solaar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MC Solaar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MC_Solaar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MC_Solaar\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.8455412057478627, \"rank\": 0.1807766030115568, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergey_Bubka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sergey Bubka\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergey_Bubka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sergey_Bubka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some have questioned whySnoop Dogg, 52, is involved in the sportingcompetition, he also has another major involvement in the games.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, the Gin 'n' Juice rapper landed a jobas a special US correspondent for NBCand Peacock and plans to give some 'Snoop style' to the gig.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9805821762418622, \"rank\": 0.01273934817730371, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999998686894374, \"rank\": 1.3127592860844147e-07, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rapper announced on January 1st in a press release and said: 'I grew up watching the Olympics and am thrilled to see the incredible athletes bring their A-game to Paris.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9829737951497095e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a celebration of skill, dedication, and the pursuit of greatness,\\\" said Snoop.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are going to have some amazing competitions and, of course, I will be bringing that Snoop style to the mix.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's going to be the most epic Olympics ever, so stay tuned, and keep it locked.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us elevate, celebrate, and make these games unforgettable, smoke the competition, and may the best shine like gold.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peace and Olympic LOVE, ya dig?'\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking toTime,Snoop said he was keen to take on this gig as he loves sports.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Why not?\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not why.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what I do, you know what I am saying?\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love being in front of the people.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love sports.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what I am talking about.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The network is appealing enough to understand that we deserve each other.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are gonna make magic.'\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that he is going to bring 'the fire and the smoke'.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When questioned about what exactly this meant, he replied: 'You figure it out.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am pretty sure you have been doing this sh-t long enough to figure out what I mean by that.'\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sente